": \"the 800metres\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was on in all the bars and naturally you get invested in the sport you are watching.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the bars\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not an easy thing to avoid!\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an easy thing\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But both of us really got into it.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looked like a class Games and I wanted to know how people were getting on and watched the 800m.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a class Games\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What an event.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What an event\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final looked tough.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 1500m, I was surprised by Cole Hocker's victory but the American always had a chance of gold as he is a quick finisher.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cole Hocker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.99999716