, \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"my doctor\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"a Zoom call\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew it could be the worst news.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst news\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were no pleasantries, no small talk like usual, just straight down to business.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no pleasantries\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It became pretty clear I would not be racing at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I was in shape for what I wanted to do so that part does not hurt, I just struggled to keep my body together.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"that part\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it lets you down it's easier to process in some ways.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not miss the Games because I wasn't good enough.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So what next?\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have now had time to re-evaluate and at 30 my priority has to be medical support so I am relocating to Manchester in a bid to squeeze as much as I can out of my remaining years in the sport.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [{\"begi